4 CONC Notes: Eugene M. Wells, 73 of New Haven, passed away peacefully at his home on Saturday July 2, 2011 with his family by his side after a long battle with Multiple Myeloma.  He was born in New Haven th
4 CONC e son of the late Alfred and Ethel Wells.  He is survived by his wife, Dorothy Ledbetter Wells, loving children, Tonya Wells of West Haven and Jason (Candice) Wells of Stratford; mother in law, Ruth J
4 CONC . Ledbetter, 2 brothers, Franklyn (Daisy) Wells of New Haven and Hurbert Wells of New Hampshire; 7 grandchildren and 3 great grandchildren and a host of relatives and friends.  He was predeceased by h
4 CONC is sister, Iris Russell and brother Calvin Wells.
